<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>10538</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>18382</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很久很久以前，一对鼹鼠夫妇的女儿莫莉，准备要结婚。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>18383</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>23700</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鼹鼠穆勒是最合适的新郎人选。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>23701</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29946</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，鼹鼠爸爸和鼹鼠妈妈却对他不满意。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29947</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>35427</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“难道没有更好的新郎吗？”莫莉的妈妈问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35428</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>40994</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们的莫莉一定要嫁给最厉害的新郎。”她的爸爸说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>40995</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45577</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鼹鼠爸爸和鼹鼠妈妈商量了这件事。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45578</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51924</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你觉得谁是最厉害的？”爸爸思索着，大声地问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51925</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56531</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“太阳是厉害的。”妈妈回答说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56532</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>60195</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鼹鼠爸爸去找太阳。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>60196</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68254</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哎呦！太热了！太阳，你是最厉害的吗？”他问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68255</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>75245</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不，我不是。当云过来挡住我，我就不能露出脸来了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>75246</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80255</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>云才是最厉害的。”太阳回答道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80256</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84172</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“噢，我知道了。谢谢你。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84173</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87316</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鼹鼠爸爸去找云。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87317</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>94650</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哎呦，太暗了！云，你是最厉害的吗？”他问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>94651</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101576</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不，我不是。当风过来，我瞬间就会被吹散。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101577</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106655</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>风才是最厉害的。”云回答道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106656</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111043</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“噢，我知道了。谢谢你。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111044</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113675</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鼹鼠爸爸去找风。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113676</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116274</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哎呦，我就要被吹走了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116275</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>122725</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>风，你是最厉害的，对吧？”他满怀希望地问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122726</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133381</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不，我不是。有一个人，即使我用最大的力气吹，也吹不动他。”风说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133382</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136593</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“真的吗？”鼹鼠爸爸问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136594</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145645</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“鼹鼠先生，如果你在寻找最厉害的，去找佛像吧。”风建议说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145646</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152732</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>虽然鼹鼠爸爸很累，但是他还是去找了佛像。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152733</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156657</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“最后我终于找到了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156658</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>163577</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>佛像，你是世界上最厉害的，对吧？”鼹鼠爸爸问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>163578</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>171728</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不，我不是。如果一只鼹鼠在我的脚底下打洞，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>171729</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177579</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我一分钟都站不稳。”佛像回答道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177580</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184997</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你觉得鼹鼠是这个世界上最厉害的新郎吗？”鼹鼠爸爸问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184998</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>193226</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“绝对是的！哈哈哈！”佛像大笑着回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>193227</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>197624</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鼹鼠爸爸回到了鼹鼠村。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>197625</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>203512</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“老婆！我找到最厉害的人了。”他对妻子说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>203513</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207794</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊，真的吗！”妈妈回答道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207795</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>211132</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鼹鼠爸爸接着解释。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>211133</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>217177</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“太阳说，‘云是最厉害的。’云说，‘风是最厉害的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>217178</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>225716</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>’风说，‘佛像是最厉害的。’然后我就找到了谁是最厉害的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>225717</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>229577</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是谁啊？”鼹鼠妈妈问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>229578</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>233962</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他是我们中的一员，是一只鼹鼠！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>233963</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>243193</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好了，那我们就从最厉害的鼹鼠中挑出最好的新郎吧。”妈妈回答道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>243194</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>248885</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>最后，莫莉爸爸和莫莉妈妈见了穆勒。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>248886</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>252910</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快，莫莉和穆勒结婚了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>252911</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>258655</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>说不定世界上最厉害的人正站在你身边呢？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>